1. A total of 676 patients enrolled in the open-label phase.
2. 285 patients met protocol-specified stabilization criteria.
3. These 285 patients were randomized to lurasidone or placebo.
4. 144 patients were randomized to lurasidone.
5. 141 patients were randomized to placebo.
